<p>Iâ€™m very happy to know that Shanghai TV station will start the English new program tonight.</p>

<p>I would like to take this opportunity to speak a few words.</p>

<p>I wish this program will satisfy the demands of all foreign friends who are interested to know something about our city.</p>

